      "label": "Human retrospective metastatic cohort",
      "sample_size_or_observations": "130 patients",
      "description": "Retrospective analysis of metastatic patients receiving immune checkpoint inhibitor therapy, stratified by prior SARS-CoV-2 mRNA vaccination status."
